<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.203967>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Campanulina cliftonia sp. nov. A, hydrotheca with extended hydranth, drawn from live material. B, hydrothecae showing tufted operculum. C, intertentacular web of hydranth. D, large anisorhiza. E, small anisorhiza. Scale bar: A, 1 mm, B, 0.3 mm, C, 0.1 mm, D, E, 10 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/203967/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

